Class Individual

  • java.lang.Object
    • Individual

  • public class Individual
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that is used in a genetic algorithm to comprise all of the important information about an individual that is part of the population used in the genetic algorithm.

      • toCargoSpace

        public CargoSpace toCargoSpace()
        A method to create the "phenotype" of the individual. It interprets the individual chromosome to construct and fill a CargoSpace object.
        Returns:
        newCS The filled cargo space with a packing achieved by the interpretation of the individual's chromosome.
